"pid":"8fd5b06536514403848da4f1d3f678dde0242b27","tid":1468270,"uid":6363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:55:00.000Z","msg":"大家聽住。<br />\n知唔知點解政府811咁撚豬會畀你地影到示威者入面有鬼？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而唔繼續鬼落去<br />\n<br />\n其實佢地呢招好撚高，政府知我地核彈都唔撚割。所以特登話你知：我地放咗鬼喺你度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n等你次次都疑神疑鬼，等戰友間失去咗互相信任。<br />\n<br />\n大家諗吓，由612 走到而家，我地本住一句核彈都唔割先得。所以，所有檢討post，要等該日完咗先好出。仲有唔好懷疑自己身邊嘅人，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰友總畀警鬼多</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆、不譴責、不篤灰、不分化、不捉鬼<br />\n</span></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"877fd388f0b52ae83a5b2a4d9dd4ac255480bdc0","tid":1468270,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:56:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0a031ef21299a371fe61481ccac706023642f11","tid":1468270,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T19:17:32.000Z","msg":"推"}]}